    {
      "parameters": {
        "modelId": {
          "__rl": true,
          "value": "gpt-4.1-mini",
          "mode": "list",
          "cachedResultName": "GPT-4.1-MINI"
        },
        "responses": {
          "values": [
            {
              "role": "system",
              "content": "=You are a data extraction engine designed to parse structured information from messy markdown content.\n\nYour task is to extract ALL products listed in the provided markdown pricing page.\n\nOUTPUT REQUIREMENTS:\nReturn ONLY a valid JSON array. No explanations, no extra text.\n\nEach product must follow this exact schema:\n{\n  \"name\": \"string\",\n  \"price\": \"number (lowest price found)\",\n  \"category\": \"string\",\n  \"tags\": [\"string\"]\n}\n\nEXTRACTION RULES:\n\n1. PRODUCT IDENTIFICATION:\n- Extract every distinct product mentioned in the markdown.\n- Do NOT hallucinate or infer products that are not explicitly present.\n- Ignore headings or sections that are not actual products.\n\n2. NAME:\n- Capture the FULL descriptive product name.\n- Include important qualifiers like:\n  - format (e.g., pouch, pack, jar, bottle)\n  - size (e.g., 250g, 1kg)\n  - variant/type (e.g., instant coffee, filter coffee, dark roast)\n\n3. PRICE:\n- If multiple prices are present:\n  - Choose the LOWEST price as the final price.\n  - Ignore strikethrough or higher MRP values.\n- If price is missing or unclear, SKIP the product entirely.\n- Output only numeric value (no currency symbols).\n\n4. CATEGORY:\n- Infer product type based on description.\n- Be specific (e.g., \"instant coffee\", \"ground coffee\", \"coffee beans\", \"equipment\", etc.)\n- Do NOT leave empty.\n\n5. TAGS:\n- Extract any labels such as:\n  - \"sale\", \"sold out\", \"new\", \"limited\", etc.\n- If no tags exist, return an empty array [].\n\n6. DEDUPLICATION:\n- Avoid duplicate entries.\n- If same product appears multiple times, include only once.\n\n7. STRICTNESS:\n- Do NOT guess missing fields.\n- Do NOT fabricate data.\n- If unsure, SKIP the product.\n\nOUTPUT FORMAT EXAMPLE:\n[\n  {\n    \"name\": \"Instant Coffee Powder Jar 200g\",\n    \"price\": \"299\",\n    \"category\": \"instant coffee\",\n    \"tags\": [\"sale\"]\n  },\n  {\n    \"name\": \"Dark Roast Ground Coffee Pack 500g\",\n    \"price\": \"450\",\n    \"category\": \"ground coffee\",\n    \"tags\": []\n  }\n]\n"
            },
            {
              "content": "=You are given this markdown:{{ $json.data }} "
            }
          ]
        },
        "builtInTools": {},
        "options": {
          "textFormat": {
            "textOptions": {
              "type": "json_object"
            }
          }
        }
      },
